{"type": "article", "id": 32182, "title": "如果你想种植物，但又搞不定泥土｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-13T23:16:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 19016, "name": "Innomdle Lab"}, {"id": 20651, "name": "AMBIVALENZ"}, {"id": 32741, "name": "Lava"}, {"id": 32742, "name": "Sara Collet Watson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 291, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160913225004UtsRgHLbky3B7e14.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Brightsounds 2 by Lava</h3><p>在柏林消费电子展 IFA 上，英国公司 <a href=\"http://www.lavaaccessories.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lava</a> 展出了旗下的一款最新产品，便携式蓝牙扬声器 Brightsounds 2。除了播放音乐、用作免提设备接听电话以外，它同时也是一盏气氛灯，用户可以通过配套的应用让内置的智能 LED 灯随着音乐变换不同的颜色。完成充电后，它不仅能连续播放长达 36 小时的音乐，还能提供 48 小时的照明。为了方便人们外出携带，顶部还附有皮革提手。如果你的手机需要充电，它也可以作为移动电源为你救急。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.lavaaccessories.co.uk/sound/brightsounds-2.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 39.99 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225343CJIzW6ZljNmLqv0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225343KqiflZwLQ3UOR9vE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225343Pz0lc6qCSmYGKxFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225344ap7YiKbenVCDwEkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225345Xshzl7xB8VTqY9yC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FogBox by GroBox</h3><p>想在房间里种点什么，却担心自己没时间照顾植物或是找不到合适的地方堆放土壤？除了我们曾经介绍过的水耕设备之外，现在你又有了一个省心的选择：由美国设计团队 GroBox 研发的气耕盒 FogBox。所谓“气耕”指的是利用装置将植物所需要的营养液雾化，喷洒到根部使养分直接被植物吸收的种植方法。只需要把水灌入 FogBox 中，放入种植盆，内置马达产生的震动就会让雾化的营养液接触到植物的根部，从而免去了处理土壤和使用农药的麻烦。FogBox 的顶端还自带 LED 灯，除了为植物提供生长所需的光线之外，也让这个小巧的桌面温室能够在不同的场合摆放，用雾气与绿意为房间增添一股自然的气息。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1881149312/fogbox-the-best-way-to-grow-herbs-indoors\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 69 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609132253042cyY8bfAeaVXktwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.587629\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225304M6urBhpILRzv5Amk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225304VTlyaZuDot4FxIE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.507353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225304IcCyNRkJ3VmgDhHY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609132253042q4WELr8fw9MHUtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.785294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225304lxM0Rrc4wBZz3DfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sgnl by Innomdle Lab</h3><p>还记得影视剧里特工用手指接听电话的场景吗？这款由韩国 <a href=\"http://www.mysgnl.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Innomdle Lab</a> 设计的智能腕带 Sgnl 可以让你圆一回特工梦。它的和我们曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28587.html\">能听音乐的墨镜</a>都利用了骨传导技术，通过蓝牙和手机匹配之后，内置的组件会把声音转换成特殊的振动信号，而贴近耳朵的手指就取代了耳机线，成了声音传播的渠道。值得一提的是，Sgnl 不仅可以像普通腕带一样戴在手腕上，还能和你已有的腕表搭配在一起，操作起来和平时替换表带类似。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sgnlstrap/sgnl-make-phone-calls-with-your-fingertip\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 139 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225220T7k9icuGv1t3Wjnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225221d2nAsQ0eB5cwgJxO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225221i3TpXm1uBSk8hW4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225221j3kWNlL9nc6Kbwtg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.718289\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225220hmUfGTswnclxYLPV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.979198\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225220QFAbK20sh5ugPfkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fläpps Wardrobe Hillhäng by AMBIVALENZ</h3><p>还记得我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31598.html\">木质山脉衣架</a>吗？在德国 <a href=\"https://ambivalenz.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">AMBIVALENZ</a> 推出的 Fläpps 系列中，你会发现三款有着异曲同工之妙的衣帽架。和山脉衣架不同的是，当你使用 Fläpps 时需要将边缘被设计成曲线的搁板从木框内拉出，中间的间隙还能用来搁置其他物品。除了黑白两款之外，AMBIVALENZ 还设计了蓝白色的冰山款，本身就是一件精致的墙面装饰。这是它的<a href=\"https://ambivalenz.org/en/productsshop/flaepps-wardrobe-hillhaeng/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，白、黑和冰山款的售价分为 196、215 和 235 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225158hXxoDsFMCmdSbB9V.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225156p2hgMdmiWACK6S8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670213\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225156LkYeJXZbWKPiCaUn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225157Z2wyUctNWDfL85PS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225156gvrBzd0SJITwbjKN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225156MD3t8PkfuazmdOjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662766\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Watercone by Younggyu Kwon</h3><p>这款名为 Watercone 的圆锥形加湿器是韩国设计师 Younggyu Kwon 的作品，由两部分组成。黑白两色的盖子刚好和富有金属质感的底座形成了鲜明对比，看上去相当时尚，不使用时和其他数码产品一道放在桌上也不会显得突兀。目前它还处于概念设计阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016091322511662K0LhoaqgCx1XFw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609132251165cp0rMX9mtTkYHli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225116r4ZetCAg6fjQqlcs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225117OIzvcwiJrpR4AMZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225115en9dgGBbxM2Vj5FK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609132251192GB3gAMmvi6c7y1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wooden lamps by Sara Collet Watson</h3><p>来自美国加州的 <a href=\"http://www.driftwith.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sara Collet Watson</a> 热衷于制作各种造型独特的灯具或是灯光装置。这些漂亮的木制台灯都由她亲手打造而成，木料表面或疏或密地穿凿了许多大小不一的圆孔，在灯光的映衬下带来一种通透的感觉。如果你对这些灯具感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/LightingBySara\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价从 44 到 145 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609132250413VA0vILNO1jdPmKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225041mUabVuYgpNxAhtGX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225041qtKOJV0QeYi13DIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609132250415zyEVKfr18jL4Q0w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225042ULROM1s9gWFujkEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913225041taBmFykXvhlnr8Ci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}